{
  "stem": "15694.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And at one evening, I went back home-- or rather where we were going to eat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I saw a group of dancers arrive at that [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Beautiful girl.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Beautiful girls.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I looked at one in particular, and she looked back, and I was young and a-- a-- [LAUGHS] immediately a flame.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But it was only seconds I saw her, and then she gave a short smile and you went-- she went inside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I thought, why wasn't I rich and grown up, that I could follow her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I suppose not everybody-- although it was a very large flat, but it was their decision, you see.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm-- I'm only a youngster.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't-- you know, decision-- decisions were made by the grownups.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It seemed sort of logical.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I didn't think about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, there-- there would have possible been enough place for the four of us, but-- well, for a length of time, I'm sure that everybody, even relations, think, well, we would be a bit crowded, and so they dispersed us as good as-- it is-- it was suiting them.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It suited us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, I went inside, and I couldn't get the girl out of my mind.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, the next day when I-- they were-- they were soon gone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I go into more details in my book about that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But sort of taking heed of the comparatively short time we have.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I sort of shorten my story a little bit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in that case I must-- now I already have shortened it so far, that I haven't told you about the hoaxes which are in the book.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
